Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.97,OP,,0,0,0,,在街角影照出的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:23.31,OP,,0,0,0,,那寂寞的身影 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:28.90,OP,,0,0,0,,聽到 再見 這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:35.67,OP,,0,0,0,,完全令我無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:49.65,OP,,0,0,0,,連警報聲 也像打鼓般一下一下拷進我心裡就像引誘我流眼淚的搖籃曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:55.76,OP,,0,0,0,,打起精神 別再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:01:01.22,OP,,0,0,0,,明天到了 一切都會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:06.90,OP,,0,0,0,,打起精神 別再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:16.17,OP,,0,0,0,,向著新吹起的風      Smile again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘！啊 戀愛紙娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我搬來這城市 已經多久了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然還有許多事我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,卻有一件事 我十分清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,早上六時半
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的同班同學天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因早上的跑步運動而肯定會經過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是 五寸釘光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 一定要讓小茜小姐看到我清爽的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 五寸釘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是每天都經過這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼好的早上 跑在這路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我總覺得會發生什麼好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那 明天也能在這裡見面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 這樣的跑步運動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,讓它成為 我與你每天的功課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,從昨晚開始就在人家大門口幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你這人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 看著我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 你剛才有踩到了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,（錯覺吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 剛才叫我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒叫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是我聽錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我重頭看到尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是非常不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其實 像你這種為了不能實現之愛\N而苦惱的人我有很合適的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔你是商人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是為了煩惱的人 而四出販賣秘密商品的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有些什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個 來來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,紙娃娃 十二張套裝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,紙娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在上面寫上命令 再貼在別人背上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,被貼上的人就會按命令列動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是效果只限一張一次而已 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,（免費給我）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（用一萬日元買）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（二百日元讓給我）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（用八千日元買）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,最後 我花了五千日元買下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個真的有用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好 下一個早乙女亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,（掉下來滾一邊去）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 早乙女同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,突然間手一松的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 不走運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 這還不能知道是否真的有用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 吃飯吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘 你在這幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不快點的話 就沒麵包了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你臉色好差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 雖然我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 提起精神來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,弄壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,又是亂馬啦 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能小心點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,（現在立即遇上壞事）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這是真的有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,天道茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然一直以來 你對我來說\N都是伸手不及的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,今天開始 就成為我操縱的娃娃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,（請跟我愉快地交往吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心意我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,九能前輩 你想在這幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,刺刺刺刺刺…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 你不動手又怎麼過招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我刺 我刺 我刺…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,刺刺刺刺刺…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我寫的是跟我愉快地交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這不就是愉快的交手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,愉快地交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,終於逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下次一定要注意會妨礙到我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,說起礙事的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是早乙女！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（跟小茜小姐吵架）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,上課時你去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,出去了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你藏著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 別欺負弱者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜小姐 保護了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟小茜沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不能就手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我都說我沒欺負他啦 你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,誰是笨蛋啦 誰是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 別自行吵起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我都還沒貼上去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你滾一邊去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,（明天請跟我約會）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘 明天星期六下午你有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要跟我約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是五寸釘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,太高興了 太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然能跟小茜小姐約會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想想總覺得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信 那傢伙竟然會約會他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,跟小茜小姐約會 去哪裡好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 首先去茶座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,開心嗎 小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 兩人終於成為公認的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,來 試試看抓著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真是相配的一對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,清新的年輕人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直是人如其心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小…小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然後兩人終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你工作辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我有藥在身的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙意外地好色嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去那公園休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先去那邊準備好水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 那傢伙跑哪兒去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,來遲了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來 吃了它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她錯吃安眠藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,（請起來吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 還是好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,非常有效的符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,符咒 要怎麼用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在上面寫上東西 然後貼在背上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,願望就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,（跑來看看吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說他把那東西用在小茜身上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,來人啊 阻止我跑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腳停不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,別胡說了 那怎麼可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是人就能讓自己的雙腳停下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,（停下來）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還有兩張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,混帳 哪有人說停就停啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜 可以進來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一會兒就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 我現在正在溫習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 你正在溫習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是佩服 佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的話就快出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了 好好努力溫習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你也多少溫習一下好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,緊張得睡不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是重要的約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要睡得著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,（能夠熟睡）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要遲到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚還是沒能把它弄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啦 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你看著哪兒跑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘那傢伙怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,約會不是今天嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 我回去了啊 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘 今天的課已經上完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,關於今天的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是昨天不是說明天嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜 要走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 明天見囉 五寸釘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你的這些東西還真有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 好好看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你寫了明天跟我約會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要約會也就永遠是明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就永遠也不能約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是呆子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙要去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,難道他還有？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,最後一張 是最後一張了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜 出世了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我們倆的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 我愛你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜 我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再離開你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一生也不會離開你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,五寸釘是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,給我等等 五寸釘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不特別討厭五寸釘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（請別討厭我）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,幾分鐘後的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,才發現應該寫上 請喜歡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.58,0:23:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說能讀取別人心事的謎之少年•覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他為了去見小茜 決定了要下山
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白小茜的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,敬請期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:53.66,ED,,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:59.01,ED,,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話 這段戀情就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:01.51,ED,,0,0,0,,太愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:07.64,ED,,0,0,0,,不能跟你相見 但我的心情 卻追著你而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:15.48,ED,,0,0,0,,想像著你在跟什麼人見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:22.58,ED,,0,0,0,,又來又往 多餘的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.24,ED,,0,0,0,,求求你 有誰能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:30.59,ED,,0,0,0,,說我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:34.25,ED,,0,0,0,,能變得幸福的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:38.51,ED,,0,0,0,,你已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:42.31,ED,,0,0,0,,打開未來的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:46.63,ED,,0,0,0,,只需要POSITIVE的想法而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:55.64,ED,,0,0,0,,腦子是明白的 可是心卻亂了
